title: Clearings of Reichsbank for Germany
notes:
Series Is Presented Here As Two Variables--(1)--Original Data, 1883-1927 (2)--Original Data, 1923-1935. Erlvisverklag Is Included In 1923 Data And Data Since March, 1927. Rapid Clearing Figures Are Included In 1923-1935 Data. Source: Die Deutschen Abrechnungstellen For 1923-1934 Data; Wirtschaft Und Statistik, For 1935 Data.

This NBER data series m12027b appears on the NBER website in Chapter 12 at http://www.nber.org/databases/macrohistory/contents/chapter12.html.
